---
title: Homemade rocket pesto orzotto with charred courgettes and tomato salad
description: What's an orzotto? Well it's like a risotto but instead of using rice, we're making it with orzo, tiny grains of rice-shaped pasta. It's a lovely HelloFresh twist we're sure you'll want to try again!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/homemade-rocket-pesto-orzetto-wk39-c1e197ea.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/homemade-rocket-pesto-orzetto-wk39-65910fd9.pdf
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 30 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/homemade-rocket-pesto-orzetto-wk39-59834f6b053468160d660bd3
